{
  "stem": "22869.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I would have never wanted him to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this learning-- what I learned from that and the different human being that it made out of me, is worth to me millions of dollars.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because of what I went through has taught me a lessons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "First of all, never to lose your head, no matter what the situation is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have never in my life worried if I miss a plane, if I sleep over a station, because there's no hotel or there is temporarily no food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Nothing shakes me out of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I know I close my eyes for a minute, and I look back where I was over 50 years ago, and I said, nothing can measure up to do this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when I open my eyes, I know I have it better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I would say that faith and belief in God is my second nature, so to say.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I-- I don't pat myself on the shoulder and say to myself, it's your doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, I created that faith.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Where it comes from, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Faith is not something you can describe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I just know that I believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I know, from the previous thing that I mentioned to you, especially with the bullets flying around me, that there was a guardian angel sent by God to catch all these bullets and not let them penetrate me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, of course, a hundred different incidents, even the thought of taking charcoal and grind it to make your own prescription might also be a nuance of a-- of a good angel giving me the thought.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Hey, do that, and maybe that will save you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You grasp, so to say, in danger at a straw.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
